    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Mesodorylaimus bomdillaensis n. sp. A: Entire female. B: Anterior region. C: Anterior end showing amphid. D: Expanded part of pharynx. E: Female genital system. F: Vulval region. G: Female posterior region." ;
